01:30:27,780 --> 01:30:29,698
<font color="#808080">(BOTH GRUNTING)</font>

1103
01:30:53,181 --> 01:30:56,224
- Ah! <font color="#808080">(SCREAMING)</font>
- <font color="#808080">(GRUNTING)</font>

