01:31:13,826 --> 01:31:15,786
- Thanks.
- No problem.

1108
01:31:17,288 --> 01:31:21,583
- My dog, he, uh... he just...
- Yeah, he's a chimera.

1109
01:31:21,667 --> 01:31:23,794
He came with you from Lorien.

1110
01:31:23,878 --> 01:31:26,254
